Welcome to 29 test Complet TOEIC® corrigé, operated by Practice To Success PTS.

This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile application, available on the Google Play Store.

⸻

Information Collection and Use

Our application does not collect or store any personally identifiable information from users.

However, the application may use third-party services that collect information used to identify you. Examples of such services include:
	•	Google Play Services
	•	Google Analytics for Firebase

These third-party services have their own privacy policies, which we encourage you to review.

⸻

Advertising and Analytics

Our app may display third-party advertisements to support development and maintenance.
These ads may use limited device information (such as advertising IDs) but do not collect personal information.

Analytics services may collect anonymous usage data to help us improve the app’s quality and user experience.

⸻

Data Security

We take all reasonable measures to protect your information and ensure that no personal data is stored or processed beyond what is necessary for the app’s functionality.

⸻

Children’s Privacy

Our application is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect any personal information from children.

⸻

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
Any changes will be posted on this page, and you are advised to review this policy periodically.

⸻

Contact Us

